edgenote638.thumbnail_url = 'http://remley.wcbn.org/ihih-msc/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Artboard-2-Copy.jpg'
edgenote638.content = '<h3><img src="http://remley.wcbn.org/ihih-msc/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Screen-Shot-2016-02-03-at-1.56.07-PM.jpg" alt="Screen Shot 2016-02-03 at 1.56.07 PM" width="560" height="315" class="size-full wp-image-842 aligncenter" srcset="http://remley.wcbn.org/ihih-msc/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Screen-Shot-2016-02-03-at-1.56.07-PM-300x169.jpg 300w, http://remley.wcbn.org/ihih-msc/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Screen-Shot-2016-02-03-at-1.56.07-PM.jpg 560w" sizes="(max-width: 560px) 85vw, 560px" /></h3><p>The stock of FDI from China to Ethiopia was 58.5 million US dollars while the total Chinese FDI stock reached $403 million in 2010. Out of the 413 Chinese companies operating in Ethiopia, 69% are privately owned.</p><p><img src="http://remley.wcbn.org/ihih-msc/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Screen-Shot-2016-02-03-at-1.56.20-PM.png" alt="" width="557" height="287" class="size-full wp-image-843 aligncenter" srcset="http://remley.wcbn.org/ihih-msc/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Screen-Shot-2016-02-03-at-1.56.20-PM-300x155.png 300w, http://remley.wcbn.org/ihih-msc/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Screen-Shot-2016-02-03-at-1.56.20-PM.png 557w" sizes="(max-width: 557px) 85vw, 557px" /></p><h3></h3>
'
